,"c":"وَإِذَا","d":"wa-idhā","e":"And when","i":"۞ وَاِذَا"},{"b":"0.77","h":"1.66","c":"رَأَيۡتَهُمۡ","d":"ra-aytahum","e":"you see them","i":"رَاَيۡتَهُمۡ"},{"b":"2.0","h":"3.48","c":"تُعۡجِبُكَ","d":"tuʿ'jibuka","e":"pleases you","i":"تُعۡجِبُكَ"},{"b":"3.1","h":"5.17","c":"أَجۡسَامُهُمۡۖ","d":"ajsāmuhum","e":"their bodies","i":"اَجۡسَامُهُمۡ​ ؕ"},{"b":"5","h":"8.7","c":"وَإِن","d":"wa-in","e":"and if","i":"وَاِنۡ"},{"b":"6.1","h":"10.03","c":"يَقُولُواْ","d":"yaqūlū","e":"they speak","i":"يَّقُوۡلُوۡا"},{"b":"7.0","h":"11.53","c":"تَسۡمَعۡ","d":"tasmaʿ","e":"you listen","i":"تَسۡمَعۡ"},{"b":"7.8","h":"12.78","c":"لِقَوۡلِهِمۡۖ","d":"liqawlihim","e":"to their speech","i":"لِقَوۡلِهِمۡ​ ؕ"},{"b":"9.5","h":"16.1","c":"كَأَنَّهُمۡ","d":"ka-annahum","e":"as if they (were)","i":"كَاَنَّهُمۡ"},{"b":"11.1","h":"18.38","c":"خُشُبٞ","d":"khushubun","e":"pieces of wood","i":"خُشُبٌ"},{"b":"12.6","h":"20.13","c":"مُّسَنَّدَةٞۖ","d":"musannadatun","e":"propped up","i":"مُّسَنَّدَةٌ   ​ؕ"},{"b":"15.0","h":"24.1","c":"يَحۡسَبُونَ","d":"yaḥsabūna","e":"They think","i":"يَحۡسَبُوۡنَ"},{"b":"16.2","h":"25.8","c":"كُلَّ","d":"kulla","e":"every","i":"كُلَّ"},{"b":"16.8","h":"26.84","c":"صَيۡحَةٍ","d":"ṣayḥatin","e":"shout","i":"صَيۡحَةٍ"},{"b":"17.8","h":"28.46","c":"عَلَيۡهِمۡۚ","d":"ʿalayhim","e":"(is) against them","i":"عَلَيۡهِمۡ​ ؕ"},{"b":"19.3","h":"32.74","c":"هُمُ","d":"humu","e":"They","i":"هُمُ"},{"b":"19.7","h":"33.17","c":"ٱلۡعَدُوُّ","d":"l-ʿaduwu","e":"(are) the enemy","i":"الۡعَدُوُّ"},{"b":"20.7","h":"34.92","c":"فَٱحۡذَرۡهُمۡۚ","d":"fa-iḥ'dharhum","e":"so beware of them","i":"فَاحۡذَرۡهُمۡ​ ؕ"},{"b":"22.4","h":"38.3","c":"قَٰتَلَهُمُ","d":"qātalahumu","e":"May destroy them","i":"قَاتَلَهُمُ"},{"b":"23.9","h":"40.37","c":"ٱللَّهُۖ","d":"l-lahu","e":"Allah","i":"اللّٰهُ​"},{"b":"27.","h":"43.9","c":"أَنَّىٰ","d":"annā","e":"How","i":"اَنّٰى"},{"b":"28.","h":"45.99","c":"يُؤۡفَكُونَ","d":"yu'fakūna","e":"are they deluded","i":"يُـؤۡفَكُوۡنَ"}],"a":{"g":"And when you see them, their forms please you, and if they speak, you listen to their speech. [They are] as if they were pieces of wood propped up - they think that every shout is against them. They are the enemy, so beware of them. May Allah destroy them; how are they deluded?"}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.08","h":"0.67","c":"وَإِذَا","d":"wa-idhā","e":"And when","i":"وَاِذَا"},{"b":"0.9","h":"1.8","c":"قِيلَ","d":"qīla","e":"it is said","i":"قِيۡلَ"},{"b":"1.5","h":"2.74","c":"لَهُمۡ","d":"lahum","e":"to them","i":"لَهُمۡ"},{"b":"2.0","h":"3.65","c":"تَعَالَوۡاْ","d":"taʿālaw","e":"Come","i":"تَعَالَوۡا"},{"b":"3.1","h":"5.39","c":"يَسۡتَغۡفِرۡ","d":"yastaghfir","e":"will ask forgiveness","i":"يَسۡتَغۡفِرۡ"},{"b":"4.3","h":"7.14","c":"لَكُمۡ","d":"lakum","e":"for you","i":"لَـكُمۡ"},{"b":"4.9","h":"8.33","c":"رَسُولُ","d":"rasūlu","e":"(the) Messenger","i":"رَسُوۡلُ"},{"b":"5.8","h":"10.04","c":"ٱللَّهِ","d":"l-lahi","e":"(of) Allah","i":"اللّٰهِ"},{"b":"6.6","h":"11.1","c":"لَوَّوۡاْ","d":"lawwaw","e":"They turn aside","i":"لَـوَّوۡا"},{"b":"7.4","h":"12.44","c":"رُءُوسَهُمۡ","d":"ruūsahum","e":"their heads","i":"رُءُوۡسَهُمۡ"},{"b":"11.2","h":"14.4","c":"وَرَأَيۡتَهُمۡ","d":"wara-aytahum","e":"and you see them","i":"وَرَاَيۡتَهُمۡ"},{"b":"12.6","h":"16.58","c":"يَصُدُّونَ","d":"yaṣuddūna","e":"turning away","i":"يَصُدُّوۡنَ"},{"b":"13.8","h":"18.67","c":"وَهُم","d":"wahum","e":"while they","i":"وَهُمۡ"},{"b":"15.3","h":"20.06","c":"مُّسۡتَكۡبِرُونَ","d":"mus'takbirūna","e":"(are) arrogant","i":"مُّسۡتَكۡبِرُوۡنَ"}],"a":{"g":"And when it is said to them, \"Come, the Messenger of Allah will ask forgiveness for you,\" they turn their heads aside and you see them evading while they are arrogant."}},"6":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.6","c":"سَوَآءٌ","d":"sawāon","e":"(It) is same","i":"سَوَآءٌ"},{"b":"2.6","h":"2.74","c":"عَلَيۡهِمۡ","d":"ʿalayhim","e":"for them","i":"عَلَيۡهِمۡ"},{"b":"3.7","h":"4.48","c":"أَسۡتَغۡفَرۡتَ","d":"astaghfarta","e":"whether you ask forgiveness","i":"اَسۡتَغۡفَرۡ